  "text": "LG and KS suspended sediment loads were calculated from suspended sediment concentrations (section 2.2) multiplied by discharge at each logged time point [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . A minimum, discharge-weighted mean, and maximum concentration for each PP phase (\u03bcg g \u00c01 dry sediment; section 2.4.2)",
